Valgrind usage 

valgrind  --tool=helgrind  ./a.out   // for syncronization issue
valgrind  --tool=memcheck  ./a.out   // for memory leak issue


valgrind --tool=callgrind --simulate-cache=yes program-to-run program-arguments

https://web.stanford.edu/class/archive/cs/cs107/cs107.1222/resources/callgrind


https://www.it.uc3m.es/pbasanta/asng/course_notes/helgrind_tool_en.html
